Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:38.93,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Hey! It’s time for breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.52,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:46.36,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Alola!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:54.32,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know where Meltan is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:15.61,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Meltan! No eating this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:18.14,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Your breakfast’s over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:34.53,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Oh! An Explosion of smiles, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:38.33,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Um, listen, Meltan just \N went for the frying pan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:42.84,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,It ate another one?! \N Burnet’s gonna be so disappointed when she hears...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:44.37,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,This is the fourth one-roto...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:47.25,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Don’t worry! \N We saved it just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:51.72,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Don’t scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:54.01,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Speaking of, \N where is Professor Burnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:56.12,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,She’s at Aether Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:59.26,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Ms. Lusamine had a request for her.{His use of "tanomaregoto" here seemed just out of place enough that I thought it might be another move reference... It wasn't. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.01,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,Be careful with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:04.39,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:09.16,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,Young Master Gladio, \N please treat my documents with a bit more care!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:12.02,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Are the documents from Dad’s \N experiments really here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.58,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:19.58,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,After the accident, I carried all of \N Professor Mohn’s documents down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:23.41,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,The President attempted to have \N all of his research sealed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:24.96,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Why would she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:29.54,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Mom tried to seal off all his data on Ultra Holes? \N I can’t believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:34.33,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,It was understandable. The shock and sadness \N from the professor’s death made her—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.80,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Father is alive! {Timed both of these lines together even though Gladio's starts a little later. - Toa}{I approve. I would have done the same. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.80,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dad is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.96,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:40.77,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,You cannot imagine my joy \N when I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:46.31,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,I need a tissue...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:50.61,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,Isn’t this... \N Oh, how nostalgic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.44,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Father...
Comment: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:55.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:36.25,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,Professor Mohn was \N an outstanding scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:39.49,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,With his exceptional talent \N and leadership,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:43.15,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,he led our research team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.48,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:03.11,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.57,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Mohn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:11.36,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.48,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.71,Main,Wicke,0,0,0,,Excuse us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:26.58,Main,Wicke,0,0,0,,We’ve had the Aether Foundation branches in each region \N look into missing person cases... {Wonder if we'll see any of these in Pocket Monsters 2019. - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.55,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,And what were the results?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:32.68,Main,Wicke,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we’ve received \N no helpful information as of yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.56,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.69,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,The search has only just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.49,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:44.89,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,What about you? Did you find \N Professor Mohn’s research documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.22,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Sauboh is looking for them for me.{You know, it's rather bizarre how both in the game and the anime, everyone just COMPLETELY forgave him for his blatant evilness... -Starfish}{throwing away Grass Owl, while unspeakably evil, is technically NOT illegal}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.46,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Gladio and Lilie are helping him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:52.08,Main,Wicke,0,0,0,,The two of them are eager to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:53.95,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Of course they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:56.95,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:02.21,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Dad is alive! He’s still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:07.58,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Hāpu'u... The Island Queen \N on Poni Island told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:10.01,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,...that the reason we didn’t meet him \N inside Kapu-Rehire’s mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.97,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}...was because he’s still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:18.74,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,I’d never seen Gladio that happy before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:23.10,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,That was when I realized \N how wrong I had been.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.11,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.03,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Ever since that accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:32.03,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,I never told Gladio or Lilie \N anything about Mohn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:38.62,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,It never even occurred to me just \N how dearly they longed for their father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.63,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.49,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:49.17,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,There’s something I want to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:52.14,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,We’ll handle this. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:52.64,Main,Wicke,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:14.12,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.25,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.74,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.77,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Mohn’s...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:57.12,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Your father’s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.80,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,It was this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:16.05,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Mohn was very passionate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:21.55,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,As researcher, father \N and husband alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:22.81,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,He was an admirable man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:28.07,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,He was also quite the dreamer... \N The kind of person who’d believe in fairy tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.32,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Gladio. Lilie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:37.52,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,I’ll entrust you with this room, \N until he comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.83,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:43.49,Main,James,0,0,0,,That is a splendid idea, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:44.69,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.16,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.81,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,A Z-Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:11.48,Main,James,0,0,0,,I was told he received it from \N the Island King, Mr. Hala...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:16.86,Main,James,0,0,0,,...back when he moved to the Alola Region \N to work on his Ultra Hole research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.37,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:23.73,Main,James,0,0,0,,The master was an incredibly gifted \N Pokémon Trainer, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:27.21,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Mother, where is \N Father’s Pokémon now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:33.25,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Well, it disappeared \N after the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:37.04,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,If only I’d taken better care of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:41.64,Main,James,0,0,0,,You had just gone through \N a terrible shock at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.14,Main,James,0,0,0,,It is not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:47.22,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,But {\i1}it{\i0} had gone through \N a shock, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:51.02,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Its partner had just vanished \N without warning, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:55.40,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,And yet, I was so caught up \N in my own sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:57.91,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,...that it clouded my judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.42,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,If I’d paid better attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:05.61,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,it might not have taken me so long to realize \N that Mohn might still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.54,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.21,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I was still but a baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:15.39,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,so I don’t remember anything \N about Father or the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:19.55,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,But now I understand how you felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.01,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Please, don’t blame yourself so harshly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:25.23,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.94,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,You two really saved me back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.04,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,My little troublemaker, Gladio...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:35.23,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,...and my cute little baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.53,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I’m not a baby anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:43.94,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Geez! Why do children \N have to grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:50.00,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Lilie, I think you should keep this \N until we find Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.11,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:52.78,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Oh, that’s a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:55.43,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,You should consult \N the Island King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:57.08,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,V-Very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:04.71,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Snowball, \N I might be getting a Z-Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:06.02,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:12.26,Main,James,0,0,0,,Oh, she seems to be \N quite excited at the prospect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:16.60,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,What a relief! I will go speak with Mr. Hala \N as soon as possible tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.48,Main,James,0,0,0,,What seems to be the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:45.60,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pocket Monsters Sun & Moon!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:47.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.44,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’ll get Pokémon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:12:01.01,Main,James,0,0,0,,Why, if it isn’t the Magearna that \N the master had been looking after!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.44,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Magearna?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:03.16,Main,James,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:08.63,Main,James,0,0,0,,She is an artificial Pokémon created long ago \N by the scientists in a foreign land,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.84,Main,James,0,0,0,,according to the master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:12.29,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Artificial Pokémon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.92,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,When Mohn first met this one \N on his travels,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:20.03,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,it was rusting in the corner \N of an antique shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.39,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Hey, Lilie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.86,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Why did you open this door \N all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.89,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Hmm... I’m not quite sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:38.52,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Supposedly, Magearna was created \N to look after the princess of that kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:42.93,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,So apparently, when Mohn \N first met her, he thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.65,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,...that this was fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.16,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.79,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Since we’d just gotten \N our own little princess, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:55.38,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Mohn tried his best \N to get Magearna to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:56.94,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,but it didn’t work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:13:00.50,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,So he had to give up on this \N present for his little princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.48,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,A present to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:05.33,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,...from Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.10,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,So this is your dad’s Z-Ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.73,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Awesome-roto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:16.28,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I hope you’ll find your dad soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.98,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:22.86,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Lilie is going to see Mr. Hala \N about that Z-Ring today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.11,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:30.26,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I wish to request that he let me \N use this Z-Ring until we find Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:32.93,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,That’s a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:36.75,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I don’t know if I’m really \N qualified to do so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:39.67,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,I’ll come with you to cheer you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:40.41,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.45,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.87,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’m coming, too, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:43.63,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Count me in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:46.01,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Well, then, \N let’s all go right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:49.01,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,This is plenty cause for \N an extracurricular lesson!{I swear, this is a school anime written by and for people who have never been to school. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:56.39,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,I remember the day I gave \N this Z-Ring to Mohn very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:14:00.08,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,He gave calm, precise orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:06.47,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,But when push came to shove, \N he provided a most passionate battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.20,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I would very much like to battle him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.95,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,If he makes it back, \N we will hold a feast in his honor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.73,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.03,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Now, Lilie...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:22.09,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Hit Mr. Hala with your wish, \N like an Aurora Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.25,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.16,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:27.37,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:29.27,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,We’re here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:31.23,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Relax, relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.46,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Be yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.60,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,You can realLilie do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:47.22,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Mr. Island King, Sir... Yesterday, I was shown \N my father’s room for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:50.10,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I do not remember him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:53.47,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,but yesterday, \N I could feel his love for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:56.24,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I felt elated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.62,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,And so, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:01.82,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I wish to find my father, \N whatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:06.39,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,In order to accomplish that, \N I wish to become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:10.91,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I’m certain that Snowball \N understands my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.49,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Before my father returns,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:19.52,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I wish to grow stronger \N with his Z-Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:26.53,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,And with this Ice-Z, I wish to \N master a Z-Move alongside Snowball!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:30.03,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,What must I do to \N receive your blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:36.29,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Your feelings have \N touched my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.79,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,This is what we will do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:43.79,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,You will attempt to unleash the Z-Move, \N Raging Geofreeze, before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:45.92,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:52.30,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Very well! I will try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:03.33,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Let us do our best, Snowball!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.99,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,That’s the spirit, Snowball!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:09.05,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Be quiet! Lilie can’t focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:09.69,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.95,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Are you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:12.95,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.58,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Snow silently fluttering down \N from the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:23.65,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Countless glimmering crystals of ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:27.04,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,O, freezing Z that covers the land...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:32.84,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Along with my heated soul, \N return now once more to the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.85,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Raging Geofreeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:48.33,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,So close...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:50.07,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,She almost had it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.57,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, Lilie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:57.89,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,If you just train and become stronger, \N I’m sure you’ll be able to pull off a Z-Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:59.78,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Satoshi’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:03.21,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,The Alola League’s drawing near, too, \N so we’ll all train every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:08.17,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,I’ll do my best, too! Seeing you \N made me want to use a Z-Move myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:12.36,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,You managed to make Z-Power manifest! \N That’s amazing in itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:13.68,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Right, Xiemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.66,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:26.93,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,No, Snowball... It wasn’t your fault \N that the Z-Move failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:29.53,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} simply wasn’t strong enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.61,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,It’s true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:36.66,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,So, I will do my best! \N I will become stronger, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.42,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Please bear with me, Snowball. {Wanted to suggest "abide" in place of "bear", but apparently "Abide With Me" is the name of a hymn, dunno if that could be seen as an unintentional reference. - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.79,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,You almost had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:50.13,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,But, young Lilie... I most certainly did see your Z-Move, \N incomplete though it may have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:55.97,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,I will give you special permission \N to wield that Z-Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:01.76,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,I suppose you may call it \N a provisional license.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:05.26,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Island King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:10.31,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I promise I will master \N the use of my father’s Z-Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.77,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.80,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’m so happy for you, Lilie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.18,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,The Island King is so generous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.98,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,The Z-Ring must have chosen Lilie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:23.66,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,You {\i1}do{\i0} have some pretty great lines \N now and again, Satoshi.{This is word-for-word the same thing he said in episode 55 at 4:52. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:29.37,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,When your training bears fruit, \N and you’ve mastered your Z-Move,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.01,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,come seek me out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:32.40,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:42.17,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Magearna... I’ve been granted permission \N to use Father’s Z-Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:47.01,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I will do my best so that \N Snowball and I can become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:53.77,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,And, Magearna... \N I wish to become friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:57.81,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,The wish Father had for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:01.03,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I wish to make it reality, \N on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:05.91,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,If all goes well, when I reunite with Father, \N you will be there beside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:10.07,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.72,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.12,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:49.33,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:55.58,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,I thought you’d be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.80,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Mother... Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.86,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,What did the Island King say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.78,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,He gave me permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:03.81,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Though it’s only temporary, \N for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:04.80,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.10,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Train hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:11.82,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Yes! I wish to master the Z-Move \N as quickly as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:12.60,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:15.25,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I just found it in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:19.46,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,It appears to be Father’s research notes \N regarding Magearna.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.61,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,He wrote in it daily, at great length...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:25.24,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,You might call it a Magearna journal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.24,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,I never knew he had that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.58,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:31.91,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Please let me take care \N of Magearna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:37.14,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Perhaps it will never move, \N no matter what I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:40.09,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Even so, I wish to make it move, \N if at all possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.29,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Just like Father wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.54,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:49.88,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,You really have become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:51.56,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Have I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:02.22,Main,Lilie reading Mohn's journal,0,0,0,,“Today, I stopped by \N a small antique shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:05.07,Main,Lilie reading Mohn's journal,0,0,0,,“and for a moment, \N I doubted my own eyes.”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:11.57,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,A Magearna was lying there \N in a corner of the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:16.49,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,It was covered in rust, \N but I could tell it was a Magearna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.93,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,It’s said that Magearna was created...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:24.88,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,...over five hundred years ago, \N by the genius scientists in a distant land.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:31.14,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,Just then, Lilie’s cute smile \N came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:34.15,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,I thought this must be fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:37.61,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,I will give Magearna to Lilie \N as a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.27,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,To my little princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.44,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:48.39,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Through Professor Mohn’s Z-Ring \N and her meeting with Magearna,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:51.79,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Lilie is starting to feel \N a strong bond with her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:54.31,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:57.57,Main,Narrator,350,0,0,,Lilie’s new dream has \N been put into motion.
Comment: 0,0:21:59.47,0:21:59.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{PokéProblem - Answer}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.35,0:23:25.08,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:28.55,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,The Pokémon I encountered \N was Magearna!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:32.45,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,It seems the Artificial Pokémon Magearna, \N which was created hundreds of years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:35.03,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,is a Steel/Fairy type.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:39.18,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Magearna, I should very much like \N to talk with you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:44.73,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I do believe the first part is fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:48.33,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,But after the “Freezing Z that \N covers the lands” part...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:53.11,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I may have been mistaken to \N follow it up with “My heated soul”.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.48,0:23:56.12,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ice isn’t hot, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:58.95,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,{\an8}I will try my best to \N make it work next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.48,0:23:57.18,Main,James,0,0,0,,Young Lady, I do not believe \N the {\i1}wording{\i0} is the problem...
Comment: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:03.25,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Hey, where in Malie City \N do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:05.71,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,We’re only there for two days and one night, \N after all... We’d better plan proper—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.71,0:24:07.35,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,I want to try some of \N their Octan-yaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.35,0:24:09.13,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,What’s that?! \N I want to try some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:11.01,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Their sweets appear to be \N famous as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:12.43,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Such as their dango \N or their botamochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:14.30,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Sounds great! \N Let’s go try all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:15.68,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I told you, we have to \N lay some proper pl—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:19.75,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Kaki, isn’t this Tosakinto yōkan \N the one that Hoshi had said she wanted to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.75,0:24:22.23,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,It is! Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.65,0:24:26.36,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Next time, on Pocket Monsters Sun & Moon:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.36,0:24:30.44,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Xiemi, Meltan, and Sandy! Lost Explorers!!
